# Reference material shipped with the repo but not intended for production.
# The /gif/ app keeps these alongside the generator for traceability, but the
# files are multi-megabyte game dumps / legacy demos and would push the
# deploy above Cloudflare's per-asset 25 MiB limit (and slow deploys).

gif/oldexamples/
gif/newexamples/

# Raw sprite bytes now live in the Garage S3 buckets (slp/ and sld/) and are
# proxied through the Worker at /api/gif/{slp,sld}/. Anything that shows up
# locally under sourcefiles/ during development should never be deployed.
gif/sourcefiles/slp/
gif/sourcefiles/sld/*.sld
